About NightLabs Maven Site Skin

    This project provides a Maven Site Skin to be used in NightLabs
    Maven projects. It picks up the visual design used on
    {{http://www.nightlabs.de}}.
    
* Introduction

    This skin is to be used like any other Maven Site Skin. For a quick
    introduction see:
    
    * {{{./configure.html}Configure Project}} - How to configure your Maven
      project to use this skin.
       
    * {{{./menus.html}Use Menus}} - How to use menus in a Maven Site and how
      menus are displayed with this skin.
       
    * {{{./links.html}Use Links}} - How to use links in a Maven Site and how
      links are displayed with this skin.
      
    * {{{./content.html}Create Content}} - How to create content for a Maven
      Site.
    
* More Information

    * {{{./favicon.html}Use a Favicon}} - How to add a custom favicon to your
