    * {{{./css.html}Use custom CSS}} - How to add custom CSS to your site.

* Maven Site Plugin documentation

    For more in-depth information about Maven Sites, visit the 
    {{{http://maven.apache.org/plugins/maven-site-plugin/}Maven Site Plugin site}}.
    
* Troubleshooting

    There are some problems generating sites using Maven 3. To make Maven 3
    site builds work, you have to define the Maven Site Plugin version 
    >= 3.0 in your pom.xml:
    
---------------------------------------
<build>
  <pluginManagement>
    <plugins>
      <plugin>
        <groupId>org.apache.maven.plugins</groupId>
        <artifactId>maven-site-plugin</artifactId>
        <version>3.0</version>
      </plugin>
    </plugins>
  </pluginManagement>
</build>
---------------------------------------
